Photo Print

2 min
overview & purpose allow your customers to print their photos in multiple sizes and help them treasure their memories, and frame their favorite moments with family and friends this product allows your customers to build their photos in the ‘print photo builder’ screen, apply additional options, and order the same photo with multiple sizes in multiple quantities then can add borders, orientation, crop, and apply many more effects key features key features of photo print products include – your customer can add borders, orientation, crop, and apply many more effects you and your customers will have a new user experience with efficient price calculation, shopping cart, and order management a print builder screen, where customers can upload their images from the ‘upload photos’ button customers can set different additional options for each picture, edit them, and print different quantities of each picture customers can use various editing tools and enhance their image quality check the product summary on the cart page
